web_snippets: Dingdong Dantes. Article ... Jose Sixto "Dingdong" Gonzalez Dantes III (born August 2, 1980) is a Filipino actor, filmmaker, and television personality.
Dingdong Dantes is a Filipino actor, television presenter, dancer, commercial model and film producer who is working as an exclusive talent of GMA Network.
